VKTX Theres preclinical data from an animal model that used ICPTs OCA as a comparator OCA failed to demonstrate a statistically significant reduction in fibrosis The trail drug CRV431 reduced fibrosis scores by approximately 43 p 0005 however in other multiple trials the results werent so robust This best preclinical fibrosis outcome is still not as good as THRbeta data coming from MGL3196 p0001 Ph2 Preclinical data tends to trend downward on larger Ph1 human trials No data on CV benefits of redux to LDL cholesterol Apos insulin sensitivity At Ph2a VK2809 had better data across the board vs other oral NASHNAFLD being tested including MGL3196 Expecting to see PH2b NAS resolution score to be as good or better with better safety profile due to smaller dosing by a large factor
